	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=185185><span id= >Thataway</span></a><br><span id=notbold>11 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Here is a quick break down of needed items:<br>Valorium Ring of Gallantry <br>MAGIC ITEM AC: +5 Str: +8 Sta: +8 Agi: +8 Dex: +8 Fire Resist: +5 Cold Resist: +5 HP: +65 Mana: +40 Weight: 0.4 Classes: All Classes Races: All Races Inventory Slot: Finger<br>Planes of Power required<br>Crafted: This item is crafted by players. <br>Valorium Ring of Gallantry (Jewelcraft, 250 trivial) <br>A Razorfiend Talon (1) Dropped <br>Yellow Diamond of Valor (1) Crafted with Non-Tradeskill, 0 Trivial <br>Enchanted Bar of Valorium (1) Crafted with Smithing, 135 Trivial <br>Planar Jeweller's Kit (1) Storebought <br>YOU MUST combine these 3 items in this kit.<br>This item may be purchased at vendors in&nbsp;&nbsp;Plane of Knowledge Noirin Khalen loc neg74, 328 <br><br>Crafted: This item is crafted by players. To make these:<br>Yellow Diamond of Valor (Non-Tradeskill, 0 trivial) you use :<br>Metallic Liquid (1) Dropped <br>Spell: Imbue Valor (1) Crafted with Jewelcraft, 0 Trivial     buy in  Freeport North, Locarme Zennix <br>Raw Diamond (1) Dropped <br><br>Crafted: This item is crafted by players. <br>Enchanted Bar of Valorium (Smithing, 135 trivial) You use:<br>Brick of Valorium (1) Dropped <br>Vial of Distilled Mana (1) Crafted with Non-Tradeskill, 0 Trivial <br><br><br>I hope this helps you all. <br></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Thatawy Gateer<br>Of the Rathe Server<br>Druid traveler of the <br>Norrath Travel Bureau</td></tr>
